<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link357386" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=357386&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F447452-i-wanted-to-know-if-there-is-any%2Fanswers%2F357386-cosmos-as-i">flag</a>
</div>
