<span id="freeTextContainer8258784237419897905"><b>Humbling vistas</b><br/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1618597059i/31189934._SX540_.jpg' height='400' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><b>
  <i>&apos;Pale Blue Dot&apos;, updated version of a photograph of the Earth, 6 billion kilometers (3.7 billion miles) away, taken by Voyager in 1990, part of the &apos;Family Portrait of the Solar System&apos; series of photographs</i>
